        "genprov_desc":"(Subpart B) This subpart applies to discharges to waters of the United States and to the introduction of process wastewater pollutants into publicly owned treatment works from any plant which manufactures veneer and does not store or hold raw materials in wet storage conditions.",
        "genprov_monitoring_reqs":false,
